
'''* Article: Dual Licensing in Open Source Software Industry. By Mikko Välimäki. Systemes d´Information et Management, Vol. 8, No. 1, pp. 63-75, 2003.'''

URL = http://www.valimaki.com/org/dual_licensing.pdf


=Abstract=

"This paper analyses how several open source companies use [[Dual Licensing]]: both
open source and proprietary licenses for one product. Three case studies based on the 
experiences of companies Sleepycat Software Inc., MySQL AB, and TrollTech AS illustrate 
the issue. Especially the legal and economic requirements of dual licensing are identified."


